               <p>I am a pawn-broker, I live in Piccadilly, the prisoner came to me and pledged this cloak with me for 10 s. 6 d. in the name of 
               <persName id="t17840114-10-person163">
                  Martha
                   Ray
               <interp inst="t17840114-10-person163" type="surname" value="Ray"></interp>
